    "updated_at": "2015-04-24T05:28:09Z",
    "body": "WebView does support setZoomFactor, it just doesn't automatically scale to the parent's zoom factor. You need to call it from within the preload script (i.e. in the context of the webView itself, not the renderer host)\n"
